      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "What do you mean by static and automatic Tor bind in bitcoin's configuration? Right now there is just one type of bind that is done at startup with a default value of `127.0.0.1:8334`. The user can change the default value but cannot switch that binding off.\r\n\r\nDo you mean to allow switching off by using `listenonion=0` and not using `bind=...=onion`?",
